title: I Can't get unchained alistar
body: I've gone through all the steps several times. But I still dont get the skin it says"There was an error accessing your youtube account. You may try the workaround suggested below." I do the steps again but the same thing happens. Has this happened to any of you guys?

replies.body: i'm trying it right now.  how long should it take for them to get back with me?

Hiya! 

If you're having trouble redeeming this skin, please [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll get the skin added to your account. :]
Don't you think at some point it would be easier to just fix the damn site instead of adding every single one manually?
